    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/5d29a28e5a003dea04bc407dfe804520.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=342 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>英勇奋战的骑士，搭配拥有魔法的神秘猫猫，在冒险途中会有什么化学反应？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/28490a3df27020626cb5f3a491a9043c.poster.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/28490a3df27020626cb5f3a491a9043c.webm?t=1772006065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/28490a3df27020626cb5f3a491a9043c.mp4?t=1772006065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《维兹之刃》是一款俯视角动作roguelike游戏。成为因被灵体附身而被放逐的流浪骑士塞拉，与罪魁祸首——一只神秘的黑猫灵体，一起深入皇城腹地，找到解除“附灵诅咒”的方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/e408683a0d60080461adf08c8f0a0003.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途中充斥着各种挑战，但这看似来者不善的猫咪似乎能给你提供帮助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据自己的攻击方式，选择黑猫灵体的技能，好好搭配，它能助你一臂之力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/66823f5e1a404565d3d1817f5e3a0293.poster.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/66823f5e1a404565d3d1817f5e3a0293.webm?t=1772006065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/66823f5e1a404565d3d1817f5e3a0293.mp4?t=1772006065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/d4bd97c30d5fdf10f4e37ecb60fcb26d.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=94 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光靠蛮力不够，《维兹之刃》有着一套完整的元素体系。使用风火雷电冰等多种元素搭配，可以让你的招式更具威力！同时，<strong>数十种武器</strong>，40种以上的纹章搭配，配合相应的元素，即可打造出你喜欢的战斗流派。发挥你的想象力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/be75075c747167101129167b87c4883c.poster.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/be75075c747167101129167b87c4883c.webm?t=1772006065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/be75075c747167101129167b87c4883c.mp4?t=1772006065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/572a5f477678d061d051e53498fe3adf.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划好你的行进路线，每个不同标志预示这你将遇到的挑战，从中获得更多的猫咪技能，或是你自己的攻击招式，又或是小憩一下回复血量。让你越挫越勇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/81df1ff7a15bd26c2c9dc68f31dad59c.poster.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/81df1ff7a15bd26c2c9dc68f31dad59c.webm?t=1772006065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/81df1ff7a15bd26c2c9dc68f31dad59c.mp4?t=1772006065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125540/extras/d4c65980a009ced75337a0132a5920d1.avif?t=1772006065\" width=780 height=94 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩时长预计10小时以上，量大管饱</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3大章节，每个章节10张及以上关卡，每扇门背后都是未知</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内的多种支线任务，探索这古老城堡的故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种武器，涵盖远程、近战、魔法等各种战斗模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >风火雷电冰，不同元素打法，给你华丽战斗体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40种以上纹章，供玩家探索并构筑适合自己的流派</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快助猫猫一臂之力^ω^</p></li></ul>",
